name: Clay County Public Health Center
tweet: Yesterday, Dr. Raghu Adiga from Liberty Hospital spoke about our rising COVID numbers in the KU Health System’s Morning Update ( https://t.co/eoukE9K5p5).   His advice? Protect yourself and those you love NOW by getting a vaccine AND BOOSTER, masking up, and staying home if sick.

name: Clay County Public Health Center
